For sale is a TAURUS MILLENNIUM PRO (PT140 pro) .40 S&W (SA/DA) with Taurus LIFETIME WARRANTY. The Sights were Upgraded to Williams FireSights. There is a Limbsaver hand grip. The feed ramp has been polished. Also included & pictured (below) are: (2) Holsters, (1) OWB Nylon belt holster, modified for the CT Laser & (1) RH Foxx IWB Adjustable holster, also modified for the CT Laser. (4) 10rd Taurus mag's w/custom over-molded textured base plates (adding 1/2" extra length to each mag),  (1) 15rd Taurus Mag w/spacer (originally from a 24/7). The Crimson Trace laser (on the gun) & it's Original Box + Warranty Card, note* it's Not yet been REGISTERED & still Has the Original 3 Year Mfg Warranty. 200 rd's rounds of BVAC 180 grain copper plated hollow point (CPHP), Boxer-primed once fired brass ammo, vacuum sealed in packs of (50). The OEM Taurus Plastic Case w/Matching #'s, Cleaning Brush & Taurus SAFETY Keys (not pictured) are Included in the sale. Less than 10 Rounds have been fired through this gun, it's spent a year in a safe as a backup to my daily carry gun. 
